settings.text:
Reach out


Whether you have questions about a program or you’re just looking to connect, I’d love to hear from you.

Info@reachyourbestlife
Reach me on social media

REACH with VICTORIA RAY

Step into who you were meant to be!
Get my free guide, “Poise and Potential,” and start confidently showing up as your best self.

For me, your development is personal!

 After struggling to feel comfortable in my own skin for years, I finally decided to do something about it. What started as a quest to conquer my own insecurities has turned into a system that has helped hundreds of my members step into who they really are and confidently show up in their lives like never before.

Online courses


Take a self-guided journey with weekly interactive lessons.

1-on-1 coaching


Dive deep into your development with personalized guidance.

DIY guides


Learn actionable skills you can easily use to improve your daily life.
Resources for every stage of the journey
My life will never be the same and it’s all thanks to Victoria!
Kate Maple
I’ve seen a transformation in every aspect of my life. Thank you, Victoria!
David Cordova
Rebecca Night
I can’t begin to express the deep transformation that occurred in every aspect of my life
Victoria showed me it was OK to be me and taught me how to love life again.
Rebecca Waters
The latest from my blog
Get started with one of my 6-week courses

Create good energy

We hear the saying “good vibes only” everywhere, but that’s easier said than done. Good vibes are not about pretending nothing is wrong. They’re about creating positive energy around yourself and what you’re doing.

An attitude of gratitude


When you come from a place of abundance and gratitude, your whole life will change. This course will help you appreciate life (even the aspects you used to dread), and you’ll see success and failure from a fresh perspective.

Who you’re meant to be

We are all unique individuals with dreams and desires. As we grow, the world around us begins to influence our identity. This course will lead you on a journey of self-discovery where you step into who you’re meant to be with confidence.

Stay Connected


Get resources, motivation, and guided activities delivered to your inbox:

settings.title: Master the Science of Secure Attachment
settings.subtitle: Attachment Nerd gives you research-backed tools to connect with your kids and cope with parenting's emotional rollercoasters.

settings.heading: Licensed therapist, author, mom of 3, and cyclebreaker.
settings.intro_text:
I created Attachment Nerd because I believe every parent deserves a judgment free, shame free space to learn and apply the science that helps us build truly secure relationships with our kids.

I’ve spent the last 19 years working as a therapist and helping people heal from wounds that came from insecure attachment experiences.I plan to spend my remaining decades helping parents prevent those insecure attachment wounds and replacing them with securely attached relationships instead.

You're not. And I can prove it to you.

settings.heading: The Secure Parenting Program
settings.description:
A 6‑week, therapist‑led program that gives you easily digestible lessons, helpful scripts, and reflection worksheets so you can master the art and science of secure parenting.
You’ll leave with fewer shame spirals and more confident, connected moments.

settings.title: Never Too Late
settings.description: Whether your child is 2 or 22, it's never too late to make repairs and strengthen your bond. Hope and healing are always possible.

settings.heading: Perfect Parenting is not a thing—Present Parenting is.
settings.subheading:
Your children are not giving you a hard time. They're having a hard time. And sometimes we are too. The goal of the Secure Parent Program is to help you learn how to stay present, even when things are hard, so that your kids learn they can rely on you, even when life is crusty, musty, and challenging.

It’s never too late to learn how to be present and connected with our kids.

Victoria Ray

Hi, I'm Victoria Ray

Founder of REACH

This is my Story

 

Growing up in a small town, I often found myself sitting on the sidelines wondering why I wasn’t like everybody else. After struggling to feel like I genuinely belonged for most of my life, I decided it was time to break free from my limitations and step into the person I was always meant to be — confident and free to live the life I’ve always imagined. 

Now I’ve turned my transformation into an easy-to-follow system that anyone can use to unlock their potential and start enjoying life like never before.
